          edges — lives below the API.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-px overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-200 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          {features.map((f) => (
            <div class="group bg-white p-6 transition-colors hover:bg-neutral-50/70">
              <div class={tile}>
